TARDIS
======

A dirt simple program for time tracking.


Overview
--------

Records the current time and project string entered by inserting into an entry
table.


Usage
-----

To create a new entry,

    $ t project "a description of the project"

To stop for the day,

    $ t stop

That's it!


Scripts
-------

There are some convenience scripts in the script/ directory.

report: how many seconds you have devoted to a project
all: all entries
clear: delete all entries


